{"title_page": "San Leandro, California", "text_new": "{{Use mdy dates|date=September 2014}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                            = San Leandro, California\n| settlement_type                 = [[City (California)|City]]\n| image_skyline                   = San Leandro Marina 07830.JPG\n| imagesize                       = \n| image_caption                   = San Leandro Marina\n| image_flag                      = Flag of San Leandro, California.gif\n| image_seal                      = Seal of San Leandro, California.jpg\n| nickname                        = \n| image_map                       = Alameda_County_California_Incorporated_and_Unincorporated_areas_San_Leandro_Highlighted.svg\n| mapsize                         = 250x200px\n| map_caption                     = Location within Alameda County\n| image_map1                      = \n| mapsize1                        = \n| map_caption1                    = \n| pushpin_map                     = California#USA\n| pushpin_map_caption             = Location in the United States\n| pushpin_label                   = San Leandro\n| coordinates                     = {{coord|37|43|30|N|122|09|22|W|region:US-CA|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type                = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n| subdivision_name                = {{USA}}\n| subdivision_type1               = [[U.S. state|State]]\n| subdivision_type2               = [[List of counties in California|County]]\n| subdivision_name1               = {{flag|California}}\n| subdivision_name2               = [[Alameda County, California|Alameda County]]\n| established_title               = [[Municipal corporation|Incorporated]]\n| established_date                = March 21, 1872<ref>{{Cite web\n |url         = http://www.calafco.org/docs/Cities_by_incorp_date.doc\n |title       = California Cities by Incorporation Date\n |format      = Word\n |publisher   = California Association of [[Local Agency Formation Commission]]s\n |accessdate  